{"id":61978,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fran%C3%A7ois_Truffaut","text":"=\"preserve\">Fran\u00E7ois Roland Truffaut (6 February 1932 \u2013 21 October 1984) was a French movie director, producer, writer, actor and critic. He was very popular in the 1960s for such noted movies as \"The 400 Blows\", \"Jules and Jim\", \"Stolen Kisses\", \"The Wild Child\" and others.\nTruffaut was born in Paris and died of brain cancer in Neuilly-sur-Seine, Hauts-de-Seine.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"France","surface_form":"French","offset":79},{"uri":"Movie","surface_form":"movie","offset":86},{"uri":"Movie_director","surface_form":"director","offset":92},{"uri":"Movie_producer","surface_form":"producer","offset":102},{"uri":"Screenwriter","surface_form":"writer","offset":112},{"uri":"Actor","surface_form":"actor","offset":120},{"uri":"Critic","surface_form":"critic","offset":130},{"uri":"The_400_Blows","surface_form":"The 400 Blows","offset":197},{"uri":"Jules_and_Jim","surface_form":"Jules and Jim","offset":214},{"uri":"Stolen_Kisses","surface_form":"Stolen Kisses","offset":231},{"uri":"The_Wild_Child","surface_form":"The Wild Child","offset":248},{"uri":"Paris","surface_form":"Paris","offset":297},{"uri":"Brain_tumor","surface_form":"brain cancer","offset":315},{"uri":"Neuilly-sur-Seine","surface_form":"Neuilly-sur-Seine","offset":331},{"uri":"Hauts-de-Seine","surface_form":"Hauts-de-Seine","offset":350}]}